  "description": "The Potions or Brewing Guide adds a visual UI with all potion recipes, ingredients, and effects, so you no longer need to search how to make, extend, or throw them. It makes potion crafting faster, easier, and more intuitive in Minecraft.",
  "body": "![BREWING POTION GUIDE](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3043199b3b68babbd8c4bd8762e393753bd3bc01.png)\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/devav\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/636bbebeeb86361b6c3672ae2811673d645ec08c.png\" width=\"200\" alt=\"Download on Modrinth\" />\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/devav/projects\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b74cf8f9bc167120468ea968ba0e77c63fdfdaeb.png\" width=\"220\" alt=\"Available on CurseForge\" />\n    </a>\n        <a href=\"https://mcpedl.com/user/devav/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0028f46ca798440db511e04046ae854c657ecb73.png\" width=\"200\" alt=\"Download on MCPEDL\" />\n    </a>\n  </p>\n\n  <p align=\"center\">\n        <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/devav\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d51d446fa425b6205dc3b08a1c9430ec31b2f59c.png\" width=\"250\" alt=\"Support me a KOFI\" />\n    </a>\n  </p>\n  <p align=\"center\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1359411?style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&color=f16436&label=CurseForge\" alt=\"CurseForge Downloads\" />\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1359411?style=for-the-badge&label=MCPEDL&color=00a859&logo=data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"MCPEDL Downloads\" />\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n# Tired of checking the wiki every time you brew?\nThis essential visual guide integrates all potion recipes directly into your game UI. Whether you're a master alchemist or just starting out, this tweak provides a clear, easy-to-read reference for every potion—including splash, lingering, and enhanced versions—right when you need it.\n\n ![brewing guide](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3aea8e3a8dd8b5da9480b6a7c0a0cfacd777a2c0.png)\n\n \n\nThe potions or Brewing Guide is missing something that we already have on the crafting table, potions guide, all the necessary ones to make our potions, increase their durability, make them throwable as you know if you are new to Minecraft or always looking for how such a potion is made in Minecraft with this texture pack that adds that information to the UI you will not need it anymore.\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n<h2><font color=\"#F0C75E\">DISCLAIMER OF LIABILITY</font></h2>\n\nIf You Are Recording And Show The Texture, Be Sure To Leave The Original <font color=\"#1FA458\">Modrinth Link</font>.\n\nPLEASE DO NOT PUT DIRECT LINK OR CUSTOM LINK.\n\n<h3><font color=\"#72D98C\">THANKS A LOT.</font></h3>\n\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/ready-crops-animated-highlighter-tweaks\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/raZ5aGa.gif\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"Download on Modrinth\" />\n    </a>\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n",
